  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    How employers are benefitting from T Level industry placements
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Examples of how businesses are making the most of T Level industry placements</p>

  </div>
</div>

